{"tid":263262,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"想你做我最後既一個女朋友☹️","createTime":"2017-05-30T00:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T08:12:07.000Z","uid":12323,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2dfe2522bf9efc008b24a5e49b549a474f6f7b3","tid":263262,"uid":12323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:18:15.000Z","msg":"同你識左年幾，個陣大家都有拍拖，到之後不知不覺咁中意左你，係意想不到咁中意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就好似淨係對你有興趣，其他女仔點好點令都冇興趣咁，呢個感覺自初戀之後就未有過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好可惜既係你有男朋友，有一排同你冇聯絡，突然你又搵返我，話擔心我，雖然唔知真定假，但我都好開心，你攬得我好實，之後仲有拖，有攬，有錫，仲成日玩我個肚，話好好攬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但你問我地係咪timing唔岩，我話我會等你，唔想錯過你，你又話自己唔係好女朋友，又話我條件好有好多女仔好過你，但我就係中意你嘛，但點都好啦，我係真心想你做我最後一個女朋友，就算你唔信天長地久，唔信愛情會長久都好，我想試下用行動去證明我真係好中意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你既幸福我想係由我比你~<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"6c4661fbb6edef95dacb63be168cc61434411255","tid":263262,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:18:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc756a47953c18ab3c14f2275498a0edc4a69275","tid":263262,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正臭雞 有仔仲錫第二個</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臭死</span></span>"},{"pid":"5becfbc5897d241b18924210caecb7641bad1e87","tid":263262,"uid":12323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:20:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正臭雞 有仔仲錫第二個</blockquote><br />\n係我錫佢嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07f7a842fcbc0b73e3b0991ee81753d1ce8e8f0","tid":263262,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T00:22:27.000Z"